{"tid":517978,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"林順潮：或與騰訊合作","createTime":"2018-01-02T23:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T08:30:57.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e539b7281d3f1008a2934371a11b32fac2cc3db3","tid":517978,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T23:55:06.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】2018年首個交易日，有19隻新股大混戰，近半公開發售已錄超購，其中獲騰訊（700）主席馬化騰入股的希瑪眼科（3309）順利跑出，孖展超購逾21倍，市傳國際配售亦已錄超購。分析指，散戶宜集中火力認購一至兩隻優質新股，希瑪看高一線，但馬化騰效應已略為減退，投資者對希瑪首日股價表現不宜期望太高。<br />\n<br />\n據市場統計，晉安（2292）、恒宇（2448）、乙德（6182）、森浩（8285）、駿溢（8350）、ISP Global（8487）、龍皇（8493）、威揚酒業（8509）孖展亦已錄超購。希瑪上周五（29日）已開招，林順潮表示，希瑪路演的反應良好，不少投資者均有意入股，最終由保薦人「拉線」及基於雙方能產生協同效應的考慮下，選擇馬化騰、思捷環球（330）創辦人邢李㷧及北京富豪趙勇為基礎投資者，又指上市前投資者新地（016）以看中醫療為國家大政策而入股。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180103/large/03ls8p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180103%2Flarge%2F03ls8p1.jpg&h=e0341c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■希瑪眼科昨開記者招待會，林順潮（中）指「未來係網絡嘅世界」。李潤芳攝<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「邢李㷧有連鎖店拓展經驗」</strong><br />\n<br />\n他指「未來係網絡嘅世界」，很高興馬化騰入股，不排除未來與騰訊合作；引入邢李㷧是因為他有連鎖店經營拓展的經驗，對希瑪有啟示及指導作用。<br />\n<br />\n同期招股的駿溢，其主席潘國華表示，公司計劃在前海發展期貨業務及培訓人才，並與當地期貨公司合作，舉辦研討會吸納客戶。<br />\n<br />\n至於孖展仍未足額、經營火鍋店「牛氣」、品越等6個品牌的嚐．高美（8371），則擬3年內在港開設8間新餐廳。主席黃毅山指，新店將會在商場為主，每間店舖回本期約11至20個月，未有進軍內地及海外打算。<br />\n<br />\n信誠證券聯席董事張智威表示，眾多新股中較看好希瑪，因其有盈利基礎，而且有增長憧憬，加上有馬化騰效應，相信對短、長線投資者均有吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180103/20263570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F20263570&d=RbdmkvV855bbdSop%2BmIP4YsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=6d93dfd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F20263570&h=cec0e924\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180103/20263570</a>"},{"pid":"00bdd7f911f6336ad08a17f7d022edeb15de6b17","tid":517978,"uid":14422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:13:50.000Z","msg":"新股，不了"},{"pid":"da898ed2a74faf653e1ab7490f58cba9fc5df026","tid":517978,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街個個痴700呃飯食 易音黎..."},{"pid":"fb50c24cba26d4889fadbbd7b2f4c1d8dc57ecf4","tid":517978,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da898ed2a74faf653e1ab7490f58cba9fc5df026","tid":517978,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街個個痴700呃飯食 易音黎..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"好伏"},{"pid":"d902f42f165f0860954ee06dfd61c5b036e957bf","tid":517978,"uid":61105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"見過鬼都怕黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f72cd986849a54ddecf2bcef02d960fd67ea5ed","tid":517978,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"呢隻好過易鑫好多既 起馬有盈利同埋市場大 唔係d咩新興產業<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd496ce9ca56ab284fccd7d47aac336eb0de5fb","tid":517978,"uid":162953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"all in 希瑪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3d7d873f2e29fbdac8f7fc8328a2c2bc5cd269","tid":517978,"uid":64647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"呢隻睇好喎 有去過佢間野就知長期full<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d67872e699c3f6f30d31de7f48c9208cad8668f","t